title: Madrid Win in Familiar Fashion
description:
In familiar fashion, Real Madrid steal 3 points at the death against Espanyol. Barcelona dominate Valladolid with a great showing from Lewandowski. And in the Prem, Antonio Conte's side keep churning out wins. What's their ceiling?
